    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a no-frills runner to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has visible cosmetic damage, significant wear, and mechanical issues that will need attention. The honest truth is this car needs work, but for the right buyer with some mechanical know-how or a project in mind, it represents a real opportunity at a very accessible price point. Grab it while it's available!",
