    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next great adventure. This stunning beauty arrives with an aura of quiet confidence \u2014 the kind of car that turns heads at stoplights and makes every commute feel like a Sunday drive through the countryside. The exterior gleams with a depth of color that speaks to careful, loving ownership, while the interior wraps you in an atmosphere of refined comfort. Every surface tells the story of a vehicle that has been cherished, not merely used. Slide behind the wheel and feel the road come alive beneath you \u2014 responsive, eager, and ready to write the next chapter of its remarkable journey. Opportunities like this don't linger. This is the one you'll regret letting pass.",
      "price": 46000.0,
